1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:01,600
Pray that you’re a woman,

2
00:00:02,200 --> 00:00:03,880
otherwise I would’ve killed you.

3
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,800
That you shot Mercan,

4
00:00:06,760 --> 00:00:09,120
that her kidnapping was your plan!

5
00:00:09,280 --> 00:00:10,280
Everything!

6
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,800
If you hadn’t married her,

7
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:15,600
if you hadn’t loved her,
none of this would’ve happened.

8
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:19,560
I waited for you to love me for years.

9
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:24,680
I watched as the man I loved fell in love
with someone else right before my eyes.

10
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:27,520
Enough!

11
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,160
Forgive me, Ateş.

12
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:33,080
What happened, Cemal?
What am I forgiving you for?

13
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:38,000
Did you know about this?

14
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,840
What happened today is my fault.

15
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:43,120
You knew and you hid it from me?!

16
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:48,240
I was going to tell you.

17
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:50,080
What were you waiting for!

18
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,440
For Mercan to die?!

19
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:52,720
I was torn, Ateş.

20
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:55,000
I gave in to my love.

21
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,800
If my daughter goes to prison,

22
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:01,840
know this: that fire of
revenge will never go out.

23
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,800
I loved Ateş very much, Father.

24
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,440
And he loved me.

25
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,880
But we could never be happy.

26
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:14,240
Every pain we lived, every
disaster, happened because of you.

27
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,520
Everything starts with my father.

28
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,600
Can we really ignore what he has done?

29
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:24,040
Shouldn’t we have moved
past all this by now?

30
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:27,080
This madness between the two
families will never end, Ateş.

31
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,640
Our love will live forever.

32
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:32,080
But we are surrounded by evil.

33
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,640
And on top of that,

34
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:38,800
the shadow of everything that happened
in the past will always hang over us.

35
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,320
Let’s get divorced.

36
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,360
My daughter!

37
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:46,120
So Ateş came to his
senses and changed his mind.

38
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,200
What I said must have had an effect…

39
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,720
Mercan got me out.

40
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,320
Mercan did, yes.

41
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:55,000
Either your daughter apologizes,

42
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,280
or she goes back to prison.

43
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,520
I’m sorry.

44
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,720
I don’t want to get divorced.

45
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,760
Did you just decide that on your own now?

46
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,600
I decided it.

47
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,360
I’ll go by myself.

48
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,880
How will this work?

49
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:21,376
When you look at me, won’t you
remember everything that happened?

50
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,200
Fine, there’s hatred all around us.

51
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,640
We won’t be able to defeat it

52
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,760
it will always stay
there, that much is clear.

53
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,200
Sometimes we’ll get tired…
Sometimes we’ll give up.

54
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:32,216
There will be times when we say we
can’t make it to the end of this road.

55
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,800
You are the most precious thing I have.

56
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,440
I will make you very happy.

57
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,720
But if I fail…

58
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,800
would you still accept
being unhappy with me?

59
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,720
If we’re going to be unhappy,

60
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,600
let’s be unhappy together.

61
